<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Crear cuenta - TaxiGE Platform</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        :root {
            --dark: #020617;
            --dark2: #0f172a;
            --gold: #f59e0b;
            --gold2: #facc15;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --bg: #f8fafc;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 12% 10%, rgba(245,158,11,.20), transparent 30%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #111827 45%, #0f172a 100%);
            color: #111827;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .nav {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 22px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 22px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold2));
            color: #111827;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .login-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
            padding: 11px 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 94px);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: .95fr 1.05fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 28px 0 70px;
        }

        .copy {
            color: white;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 9px 13px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(245,158,11,.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.35);
            color: #fde68a;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .copy h1 {
            font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 64px);
            line-height: .96;
            margin: 0 0 22px;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        .copy p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 560px;
        }

        .steps {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 26px;
            max-width: 540px;
        }

        .step {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 16px;
            color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .step strong {
            color: white;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.38);
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 30px;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        }

        .card .subtitle {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .field-full {
            grid-column: span 2;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 7px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        input:focus {
            outline: 3px solid rgba(245,158,11,.22);
            border-color: var(--gold);
            background: white;
        }

        .error {
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .submit {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold2));
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 900;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(245,158,11,.26);
        }

        .note {
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 14px;
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .bottom-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .bottom-link a {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        @media (max-width: 950px) {
            .wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding-top: 18px;
            }

            .copy h1 {
                font-size: 42px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 620px) {
            .nav {
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .brand {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .login-link {
                padding: 10px 12px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .card {
                padding: 22px;
                border-radius: 24px;
            }

            .form-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .field-full {
                grid-column: span 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
    <a class="brand" href="/">
        <span class="logo">TG</span>
        TaxiGE
    </a>

    <a class="login-link" href="/accounts/login/">Iniciar sesión</a>
</nav>

<div class="wrapper">
    <section class="copy">
        <div class="badge">Registro seguro</div>
        <h1>Crea tu cuenta y solicita acceso como dueño de taxi.</h1>
        <p>
            Primero creas una cuenta normal. Después envías tu solicitud como propietario de taxi.
            El superusuario revisará tu información antes de activar tu panel privado.
        </p>

        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step"><strong>1. Crear cuenta</strong><br>Registra tus datos principales.</div>
            <div class="step"><strong>2. Solicitar acceso</strong><br>Envía los datos de tu empresa o taxis.</div>
            <div class="step"><strong>3. Aprobación</strong><br>TaxiGE revisa y activa tu panel si todo está correcto.</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
        <h2>Crear cuenta</h2>
        <div class="subtitle">Completa tus datos para continuar.</div>

        <form method="post">
            {% csrf_token %}

            <div class="form-grid">
                {% for field in form %}
                    <div class="{% if field.name == 'email' or field.name == 'password' or field.name == 'password_confirm' %}field-full{% endif %}">
                        <label>{{ field.label }}</label>
                        {{ field }}

                        {% for error in field.errors %}
                            <div class="error">{{ error }}</div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

            {% if form.non_field_errors %}
                {% for error in form.non_field_errors %}
                    <div class="error">{{ error }}</div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% endif %}

            <button class="submit" type="submit">Crear cuenta y continuar</button>
        </form>

        <div class="note">
            Nadie recibe acceso como administrador automáticamente. Toda solicitud de dueño de taxi debe ser aprobada por TaxiGE.
        </div>

        <div class="bottom-link">
            ¿Ya tienes cuenta? <a href="/accounts/login/">Iniciar sesión</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
